<div class="title">Anxiety Reducing Mixture</div>
<div class="substance">Phenibut, Theanine & Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=ADayInForever&Exact=1">ADayInForever</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; ADayInForever. "Anxiety Reducing Mixture: An Experience with Phenibut, Theanine & Alcohol (exp66344)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Sep 29, 2009. erowid.org/exp/66344</div>

